reviewText: Almost as good as the original movie
This is movie is so bad that it's the greatest movie that ever was.  You should defiantly get your hands in a copy if you can.

This is literally just amateurish, home video footage of people outside showings of THE ROOM. If you love the ROOM as I do, don't waste your time with this. Instead, read Greg Sestero and Tom Bissell's The Disaster Artist, which is wonderful and an utter delight.
